extendedInfo.description: Enables Pro features in "Good Morning".  Install the free "Good Morning" app before installing this!Currently enables multiple alarms, reading your Google Calendar entries, and RSS News feed reader.

reviews.title: Reliable Alarm Clock
reviews.comment: Update from last year. Working fine for JB, don\'t have any reliability issues. If I had one request, then it would be to automatically enable alarms after a reboot.

reviews.title: Used to work better
reviews.comment: I love this alarm, it worked very well on my HTC phone. Now I gave galaxy s3 and this alarm behaves very strange. At times it does not talk only white screen appears. At times it does talk but can\'t snooze it just doesn\'t turn off the talking until I turn off alarm completely. Other times it works well on first snooze but second time only white screen comes up no sound. Not sure if is Samsung problem or android 4.. Would love it if the developers fix it.

reviews.title: Amazing alarm clock!
reviews.comment: Had to purchase the PRO version of this app. With the pro version, you can set multiple alarms and customize each one with a personal wake up assistant. The wake up assistant will read a personal note, your Google (or other) calendar, read an RSS feed, play an alarm, or play one of your favorite songs / tracks that you have stored on your device. Do not miss out on the best alarm clock I have tried to date!
